data.name: lblInstructions.Text
data.value: *The rules are simple. select either rock, paper, or scissors, then press "Play Round!". The computer will make a random selection, then calculate the winner. Remember, you can always reset the scoreboard by pressing "Reset Score!".

data.name: lblBettingInstructions.Text
data.value: *In order to gamble, select the amount you would like to bet, and play the game as you normally would. You start with $20, and if you run out, you can either keep playing, or you can reset the score to get your $20 back. Have fun! :D
